fields.name: Notched Lapel Jacket
fields.description: This black jacket is a versatile piece that features a tailored fit, short sleeves, a notched lapel, and a single button closure. It is suitable for both casual and formal occasions.

fields.name: Colorful Harmony Dress
fields.description: This dress features a fitted grey top and a flared skirt with layers of fabric in different colors. It is a fun and vibrant piece that can brighten up any occasion.

fields.name: Floral Finesse Dress
fields.description: This dress has a black base and bright flowers. It flatters your figure with a V-neck and a tight waist. It is ideal for dates or parties.

fields.name: Crimson Elegance Blouse
fields.description: Unleash your elegant side with our Crimson Elegance Blouse. This radiant red shirt, tailored to perfection, offers a comfortable fit while ensuring you stand out in any crowd. The delicate tie at the collar adds a touch of sophistication, making it a versatile piece for both office wear and special occasions.

fields.name: Grey Asymmetrical Dress
fields.description: This dress is a three-piece set in a soft grey fabric. The top has a unique buttoned design and long sleeves. The skirt is long and flowing. This dress is cozy and chic.

fields.name: Patterned Vintage Coat
fields.description: This coat is a statement piece with a stunning pattern. It is long and belted, with a collar and thick fabric. It has a vintage vibe, perfect for pairing with old-fashioned suitcases..
